OL,4,CHardys wine owner warns of Christmas
OL,5,Cshortage risk
OL,6, Accolade, the wine giant that makes
OL,7, Hardys, has warned that truck driver
OL,8, shortages could hit the busy festive
OL,9, season and push up costs.
OL,11,FRobert Foye, its boss, said the firm
OL,12,Fwas being hit by external staff
OL,13,Fshortages, especially among suppliers,
OL,14,Fin distribution and delivery.
OL,16,FCompanies operating in the UK are
OL,17,Fhaving to deal with a shortage of lorry
OL,18,Fdrivers.
OL,20,FFirms including Wetherspoons and
OL,21,FMcDonald's have been affected.
